{"tid":830712,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好憎陸運會","createTime":"2018-09-21T10:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T13:02:23.000Z","uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f6a04b22dda8e5355035aeb21bde35ef8feff6f8","tid":830712,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:55:31.000Z","msg":"就快就陸運會 仲記得上年陸運會lunch time果陣 <br />\n<br />\n大家一堆堆朋友咁出去搵餐廳食飯 我就一個人行黎行去禁手機又要扮等緊朋友黎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後仲要好辛苦咁搵間冇乜同校學生去既餐廳食飯 因為好怕比人見到自己一個係到食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上年我就專登坐taxi坐左10分鐘左右 離個會場都有一後距離 諗住唔會撞到人 <br />\n<br />\n點知入到間餐廳 就撞正成堆老師 連埋我2個班主任都係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其中一個班主任就問:咦 你黎到咁遠食既? 我地都係渣車黎炸喎 <br />\n<br />\n我: 係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上網check過喱間出名啊麻 <br />\n<br />\n佢:係咩? 我未聽過喎 我地都係是但揀 近會場果邊滿哂人啊 冇計啦..係呢 你一個人? <br />\n<br />\n我:唔係..我朋友黎緊..(當然係老吹架啦) <br />\n<br />\n之後我就即刻打比我個best friend叫佢坐taxi黎 我話請埋佢車錢同飯錢 但佢都唔肯 <br />\n<br />\n我唯有趁班老師傾緊計果陣就叫左個外賣坐車番會場到食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第2日陸運會我連番都冇番tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗番起真係好慘...點解上天要咁對毒拎...唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26aff69df3d2715592f233cff28f24880f879fa2","tid":830712,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:15:39.000Z","msg":"咁大個人病假都唔識請？"},{"pid":"9d6188c21a3bcb1e7529edc356fd42dd02e76e08","tid":830712,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26aff69df3d2715592f233cff28f24880f879fa2","tid":830712,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:15:39.000Z","msg":"咁大個人病假都唔識請？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim